<H1>Setting the prompt variable</H1>

<P>You can customise the prompt so that it displays your
current working directory, username on the system and the
name of the system; or any combination of these.</P>

<P>How this is done varies according to the shell 
 <A HREF="env6.html">you are using</A>.</P>

